\c 12
\s Miriami anorohwa namaperembudzi, nokuti iye naAroni vakamukira Mozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Miriami naAroni vakataura vachipokana naMozisi nekuda kwemukadzi muItiopia waakange awana; nokuti wakange awana mukadzi muItiopia.
\v 2 Zvino vakati: Jehovha wakataura naMozisi ega here? Haana kutaurawo nesu here? Jehovha ndoku\add zvi\add*nzwa.
\v 3 Zvino muurume Mozisi waiva munyoro kwazvo kupfuura vanhu vese vaiva pachiso chenyika.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha wakataura pakarepo kuna Mozisi nekuna Aroni nekuna Miriami: Budirai imwi vatatu kutende roekusangana. Vatatu ndokubuda.
\v 5 Zvino Jehovha wakaburuka mushongwe yegore, ndokumira \add pa\add*mukova wetende rekusangana, ndokudana Aroni naMiriami; ivo vaviri vakabuda.
\v 6 Zvino akati: Inzwai ikozvino mashoko angu; kana kune muporofita pakati penyu, \add ini\add* Jehovha ndichazvizivisa kwaari nechiyeverwa, \add ndi\add*chataura naye muhope.
\v 7 Asi muranda wangu Mozisi haana kudaro; wakatendeka paimba yangu yese.
\v 8 Ndinotaura naye muromo nemuromo, uye pachena, uye kwete munhaurwa dzisinganzwisisiki; iye uchaona Jehovha kuti akadini; naizvozvo makaregereiko kutya kupopotera muranda wangu Mozisi?
\v 9 Ipapo kutsamwa kwaJehovha kwakavamukira, iye akabva.
\v 10 Gore rikabva pamusoro petende rokusangana, onei Miriami ava namaperembudzi, akachena sechando; Aroni akatarira Miriami, onei ava namaperembudzi.
\v 11 Zvino Aroni akati kuna Mozisi: Haiwa, Ishe wangu, musaisa mhosva yezvivi pamusoro pedu, kunyange takaita hedu noupenzi, tikatadza.
\v 12 Ngaarege kuva somwana wakaberekwa akafa, imwe nyama yake yakaora pakubuda kwake padumbu ramai vake.
\v 13 Zvino Mozisi akachema kuna Jehovha, akati: Haiwa Mwari, domuporesai henyu.
\v 14 Jehovha akati kuna Mozisi: Dai baba vake vakange vamupfira mate kuchiso chake, haazaifanira kunyara mazuva manomwe here? Ngaabudiswe kunze kwemisasa mazuva manomwe, agopinzwa pashure.
\v 15 Ipapo Miriami akabudiswa kunze kwemisasa mazuva manomwe, vanhu vakasafamba, kusvikira Miriami adzoswazve.
\v 16 Shure kwaizvozvo vanhu vakasimuka vakabva Hazeroti, vakanodzika matende avo murenje reParani.
